STATE of Louisiana
v.
Charles H. PARKER, Jr. NO. 2018-KH-1178 Supreme Court of Louisiana. May 6, 2019

Denied. Applicant has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing.

State ex rel. Parker v. State, 15-1237 (La. 5/27/16), 193 So.3d 1155 .
